    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/21c6f98f72aa5fcc3ce85c5d486d3476.avif?t=1771940628\" alt=\"DRAFT YOUR DECK\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras_big/21c6f98f72aa5fcc3ce85c5d486d3476.webp?t=1771940628 width=1560 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your deck from over 250 upgradable cards. Open packs, discover artifacts, recruit minions, and transform your deck between every fight. Combine two elements and create something entirely your own. Every run is a different adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/dd01c789af6ac32d47c9819ece43d037.poster.avif?t=1771940628\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/dd01c789af6ac32d47c9819ece43d037.webm?t=1771940628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/dd01c789af6ac32d47c9819ece43d037.mp4?t=1771940628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/4bd6aac213fe395758f4ea3b26afd66a.avif?t=1771940628\" alt=\"SURVIVE THE GAUNTLET\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras_big/4bd6aac213fe395758f4ea3b26afd66a.webp?t=1771940628 width=1560 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twelve heroes, each bending the rules of the Gauntlet in a different way. Pick one, start with a basic deck, and fight through rounds of increasingly dangerous opponents. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between battles, spend gold in the shop — but there's never enough to take everything. Do you upgrade what you have, or gamble on something new? The opponents grow tougher, their decks get deeper. Can you survive the Gauntlet?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/90a355e5fd42d2cae59b628c61afbd41.poster.avif?t=1771940628\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/90a355e5fd42d2cae59b628c61afbd41.webm?t=1771940628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/90a355e5fd42d2cae59b628c61afbd41.mp4?t=1771940628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/e4cee98770197bfcdd56e1e101eeac36.avif?t=1771940628\" alt=\"CHALLENGE YOUR FRIENDS\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras_big/e4cee98770197bfcdd56e1e101eeac36.webp?t=1771940628 width=1560 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Grab a friend. In Versus, draft your decks card by card, then fight to prove whose build is better. In Skirmish, battle it out with random decks and see who makes the most of what they’re dealt. One tests your strategy. The other tests your instincts. This is where it counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/ea9725f2c831ea9ca2f5ad5ae38fb0d8.poster.avif?t=1771940628\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/ea9725f2c831ea9ca2f5ad5ae38fb0d8.webm?t=1771940628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/ea9725f2c831ea9ca2f5ad5ae38fb0d8.mp4?t=1771940628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six elements. Six different ways to fight. Fire burns opponents down quickly. Ice sets up massive bursts. Earth grows stronger every round. Light builds unwieldy momentum. Mystic rewards precision and combos. Shadow trades life for power. Pick two elements, choose your hero, and bring your build to the table.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218060/extras/be2dab703a0e69365a9a0755c4f9482c.avif?t=1771940628\" width=1560 height=584 /></span></p>",
